# ============================================================
# .gitignore — 论文文献仓库
# 策略: 只追踪 Python(.py) + Julia(.jl) + Jupyter(.ipynb) 源码
#       屏蔽 PDF 论文、图片、二进制数据、编译产物
# ============================================================

# ===== 论文 & 演示文稿 =====
*.pdf
*.pptx
*.ppt
*.doc
*.docx

# ===== 图片（测试用图、论文插图、截图）=====
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.JPG
*.JPEG
*.gif
*.bmp
*.svg
*.tiff
*.tif
*.webp
*.ico

# ===== Python 编译产物 =====
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.egg
.eggs/

# ===== Julia 编译/缓存 =====
*.ji
*.so
*.dll
*.dylib
Manifest.toml

# ===== Jupyter 检查点（自动保存垃圾）=====
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.checkpoint.ipynb

# ===== 数据 & 二进制 =====
*.jld2
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.npy
*.npz
*.mat
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sample

# ===== 系统 & 编辑器 =====
.vscode/
.idea/
*.code-workspace
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ===== 压缩包 =====
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar
*.7z

# ===== 日志 & 临时 =====
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
*.cache

# ===== 环境/依赖（如需可取消注释）=====
# 通常 .toml 依赖 Manifest.toml 不追踪，Project.toml 要追踪
# *.toml 已注释 — Project.toml 会正常追踪
# 若用 Conda/Poetry:
# .conda/
# poetry.lock
# Pipfile.lock

# ===== 例外：明确保留的文件类型 =====
# 不需写 — .gitignore 默认不忽略已追踪文件
# .py / .jl / .ipynb / Project.toml 会自动被追踪
